This template is used to display round ship icons.
==Usage==
===Parameters===
*<code>[1]</code>: name of the ship to display.
*<code>damaged</code>: set to display damaged icon.
*<code>size</code>: icon size, defaults to <code>50px</code>.
*<code>link</code>: icon link, defaults to ship name.
*<code>caption</code>: icon caption, defaults to ship name.
===Examples===
<pre>{{ShipIcon|Umikaze}}</pre>
{{ShipIcon|Umikaze}}

<pre>{{ShipIcon|Umikaze Kai|caption=DD|link=DD|damaged=yes|size=60px}}</pre>
